name: Canny Cambell's
description:
This project was made using Scratch and was created for the MS Paint Jam 

Story:

You are a can of soup who's lid has been taken off by a human. Your goal is to make it to the end of each level before spilling all of your soup. Good luck, and don't die ;)

Use WASD or arrow keys to move and jump around

When you reached the "Cans Stockpiled" slide that means you've won!

RocketRev - Programming

djfoxyart - Art

The Biggest Smile - Music
